<h1>Adult Day Health Centers in Massachuestts</h1>  <hr /> <div id="about-adh-section"> <div>&nbsp;</div>  <p><img alt="" class="shadow" src="/apps/_ee/files/cr.jpg" style="width: 300px; height: 200px; float: right;margin-left:15px;margin-bottom:15px;" />BaneCare Manangement offers serveral Adult Day Health Centers&nbsp;in Massachusetts for older adults requiring a safe and supportive daytime environment. Older adults can have their emotional and physical needs monitored, enjoy recreational activities and the companionship of others at our convenient South Shore locations in Weymouth, Quincy and Hingham Massachusetts.&nbsp;</p>  <p>The well-respected programs are considered an excellent choice for older adults who would benefit from a more structured routine, daily nutritional and medication supervision and appropriate cognitive and physical activities.&nbsp;</p>  <p>The center&rsquo;s mission is to provide a home-away-from-home for older adults, allowing caregivers peace of mind knowing that their family member is safe and secure.</p>  <h3><span style="color:#3399cc;"><em><span style="font-family: times new roman,times,serif;">Admission &amp; Hours</span></em></span></h3>  <p>The Adult&nbsp;Day Health&nbsp;Center&#39;s daily rate&nbsp;includes a continental breakfast, a hot attractively prepared lunch, afternoon refreshments, health monitoring by a registered nurse, counseling, activities and personal care assistance. And transportation is provided and coordinated by each center.</p>  <p>Centers open Monday-Friday, from&nbsp;7:30 am - 3:30 pm.</p>  <p>Programming hours are from&nbsp;9:00 am - 3:00 pm.</p>  <h3><em><span style="color:#3399cc;"><span style="font-family: times new roman,times,serif;">Our Adult Day Health Centers</span></span></em></h3>  <hr /> <div class="btgrid"> <div class="row row-1"> <div class="col col-md-4"> <div class="content"> <p><br /> <a href="/Colonial-skilled-nursing-home-rehabilitation"><img alt="" class="shadow" src="/apps/_ee/files/Colonial-EXT.jpg" style="width:100%" /></a><br /> <br /> <a href="/Colonial-skilled-nursing-home-rehabilitation" style="outline: none; color: rgb(17, 113, 169); text-decoration: none;">Colonial Rehab&nbsp;&amp; Nursing Center</a></p>  <p style="text-align:start">125 Broad Street<br /> Weymouth, MA 02188<br /> <br /> <strong>Tel:</strong> 781-337-3121<br /> <strong>Deborah Brennan, RN</strong><br /> Director&nbsp;<br /> <strong>Email:</strong>&nbsp;<a href="mailto:dbrennan@banecaresouth.com" style="outline: none; color: rgb(17, 113, 169); text-decoration: none;">dbrennan@banecaresouth.com</a></p> </div> </div>  <div class="col col-md-4"> <div class="content"> <p><br /> <a href="/Hancock-Park-skilled-nursing-home-rehabilitation"><img alt="" class="shadow" src="/apps/_ee/files/hancockpark-ext.jpg" style="width:100%" /><br /> <br /> Hancock Park Rehab&nbsp;&amp; Nursing Center</a></p>  <p>164 Parkingway<br /> Quincy, MA 02169<br /> <br /> <strong>Tel:</strong> 617-773-4222<br /> <strong>Deborah Brennan, RN</strong><br /> Director&nbsp;<br /> <strong>Email:</strong> <a href="mailto:dbrennan@banecaresouth.com">dbrennan@banecaresouth.com</a></p> </div> </div>  <div class="col col-md-4"> <div class="content"> <p><br /> <a href="/Harbor-House-skilled-nursing-home-rehabilitation"><img alt="" class="shadow" src="/apps/_ee/files/harborhouse-ext.jpg" style="width:100%" /><br /> <br /> Harbor House Rehab&nbsp;&amp; Nursing Center</a></p>  <p>11 Condito Road<br /> Hingham, MA 02043<br /> <br /> <strong>Tel:</strong> (781) 749-4774<br /> <strong>Deborah Brennan, RN</strong><br /> Director&nbsp;<br /> <strong>Email:</strong> <a href="mailto:dbrennan@banecaresouth.com">dbrennan@banecaresouth.com</a></p> </div> </div> </div> </div>  <p>&nbsp;</p> </div> 